author: National Geographic
description:
Join Stanley Tucci on a breathtaking, scenic journey through Italy’s most stunning and serene locations. From the energy of Rome to the peaceful charm of Tuscany, the snowy peaks of Alpe di Siusi, and the turquoise waters of the Trabocchi Coast—this is your front-row seat to the vibrant beauty and quiet, calming magic of Italy experienced through all your senses. I sensi sonno tutto. Bring on the chill vibes.
